Manual Client Install (mapped drive method)
net use Z: \\WIN-KF07TP9524F\SMS_LAB\Client /user:LAB\Administrator P@ssw0rd
cd Z:\

ccmsetup.exe /mp:WIN-KF07TP9524F.lab.local SMSSITECODE=LAB

Repair Client via PowerShell
Invoke-CimMethod -Namespace root\ccm -ClassName SMS_Client -MethodName RepairClient

Restart SMS Agent Host
net stop ccmexec
net start ccmexec

Trigger Policy Updates
Invoke-WmiMethod -Namespace root\ccm -Class CCM_ClientUtilities -Name TriggerSchedule `
-ArgumentList "{00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000021}"  # Machine Policy Retrieval & Eval
